  - Test no duplicate vehicle names
  - Test total weight > 0 (for weighted random selection)
  - Test NO_TURN_TYPES entries all exist in VEHICLE_TYPES
  - Test pickVehicleType() returns valid type (re-implement weighted random, verify)
  - Test BUS_STOP_DIST is between STOP_LINE_DIST and SPAWN_DIST
- Run tests, commit: "Add vehicle data integrity tests"

## 1.3  Car movement / update tests (target: js/vehicles.js)
- Already well-covered (stop lines, queuing, through-state, signals, etc.)
